    "pricing.about.title": "Why I built Moonli.",
    "pricing.about.text": "I’m a developer from Vienna, and for our one-year-old we were paying around €16 a month just to log sleep cycles and basic data. That never felt right. My mission with Moonli is to make this kind of support available for free to every family with a smartphone, so parenting can feel a little lighter. Moonli is not only about the baby – it’s also about the parents, their energy and their mental wellbeing. I hope this app helps many young parents clear some mental space and focus on what truly matters: their own family.",

