    "cookies.title": "Cookies & tracking",
    "cookies.intro": "On moonli.app we only use as many cookies and tracking technologies as necessary to keep the site reliable, secure and easy to understand.",
    "cookies.section1": "1. Essential cookies: These make sure the site works technically (for example language settings). Without them, many things would not run reliably.",
    "cookies.section2": "2. Analytics cookies: When enabled, they help us understand in an anonymous way how Moonli is used so we can keep improving it for families.",
    "cookies.section3": "3. Your control: In your browser and in the app you can always decide which cookies are allowed. We’re working on offering even more granular settings directly in Moonli.",
